|launched_on_android:=|caption1=}}'''Faculty Staff''' are teachers, professors, principals, and deans. They have four stats: relationship, looks, strictness, and popularity. Some reactions are based on the relationship and strictness they have. Some of the faculty members may come from foreign [[Nations|countries]], just like classmates.



== Members of Faculty Staff ==
* Principal/Headmaster (primary, secondary, elementary, middle, and high school)
* Dean (community college, university, any higher education school)
* Professor (community college, university, any higher education school)
* Teacher (elementary/primary, middle, and secondary/high school)
* Math Teacher
*Music Teacher
* PE Teacher
* Art Teacher
* ([[Nations|country's]] language) Teacher
* History Teacher

